---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 1, 2026';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Terms of Service — AllStar Martial Arts"
  description="Terms governing your use of AllStar Martial Arts' website, services, and communications."
>
  <section class="section-pad bg-white">
    <div class="container-page max-w-3xl">
      <div class="eyebrow">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl text-brand-black mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose-style space-y-5 text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the AllStar Martial Arts website, our communications, and the services we provide. By using this website, submitting a form, or engaging our services, you agree to these Terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">1. Use of the Website</h2>
        <p>
          You may use this website for lawful purposes only. You agree not to use the website in a way that could damage, disable, or impair its operation, or interfere with any other user's use of the site.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">2. Information You Provide</h2>
        <p>
          When you fill out forms or contact us, you agree to provide accurate and current information. You authorize us to use that information as described in our <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="text-brand-navy underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">3. SMS and Phone Communications</h2>
        <p>
          By providing your mobile phone number and submitting our forms, you expressly consent to receive SMS text messages and phone calls from AllStar Martial Arts related to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Free trial confirmations and reminders</li>
          <li>Class scheduling and cancellations</li>
          <li>Membership-related communications</li>
          <li>Promotions and updates from AllStar Martial Arts</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <strong>Message and data rates may apply.</strong> Message frequency varies. You may opt out of text messages at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for support. Standard carrier rates apply.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">4. Free Trial Terms</h2>
        <p>
          The two-week free trial is offered to new students only, one trial per person. The trial provides access to scheduled classes during the trial period. There is no obligation to enroll after the trial ends.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">5. Membership Terms</h2>
        <p>
          If you choose to enroll as a member after your trial, separate membership terms will be presented and signed in person at the gym. Those terms govern your membership relationship with AllStar Martial Arts.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">6. Assumption of Risk</h2>
        <p>
          Martial arts training involves inherent physical risks. By participating in classes at AllStar Martial Arts, you acknowledge these risks and agree to the waivers and releases signed in person at the gym. The information on this website does not replace those waivers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on this website — including text, photos, videos, logos, and design — is owned by or licensed to AllStar Martial Arts. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from this content without our written permission.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent allowed by law, AllStar Martial Arts and its owners, instructors, and staff are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the website or our services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">9. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent changes. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">10. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of New Jersey, without regard to its conflict-of-laws principles. Any dispute arising under these Terms will be resolved in the courts of Union County, New Jersey.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these Terms? Contact us:
        </p>
        <p class="bg-brand-gray-light p-5 rounded-md text-sm not-italic">
          <strong>AllStar Martial Arts</strong><br/>
          1166 West Chestnut St, Union, NJ 07083<br/>
          📞 <a href="tel:+19086412769" class="text-brand-navy underline">(908) 641-2769</a><br/>
          ✉️ <a href="mailto:info@allstarbjj.com" class="text-brand-navy underline">info@allstarbjj.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .prose-style :global(h2) { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', Impact, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; }
</style>
